# AUTHORS
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# CKPool Solo for Umbrel
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

## Umbrel Package & Fork
# Packaged, forked, and adapted for Umbrel by:

  Gil Bechtel
  SoloStrike.io
  https://solostrike.io

  Modifications include:
    - Docker containerization (multi-arch: AMD64 + ARM64)
    - Automated config generation from Umbrel environment variables
    - Umbrel app manifest and docker-compose integration
    - Web dashboard (Node.js log reader + REST API bridge)
    - Startup health checks and graceful Bitcoin node detection


